how to run the playbook
ansible-playbook -e component=mongodb main.yaml
ansible-playbook -e component=web main.yaml
ansible-playbook -e component=rabbitmq main.yaml

Before we do: 
go to ansible server
git clone ansible_roboshop_roles repo 
cd to repo 
ansible-vault encrypt /group_vars/all.yaml # set password to login and in all.yaml file give the username and password for the servers you need to login 
Vault password:
ansible_user: username
ansible_password: password

